sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant WebUI as Open WebUI
    participant Orch as Orchestrator
    participant ASR as ASR Service
    participant Guard as Guard Service
    participant Emb as Embedding Service
    participant QD1 as Qdrant<br/>(econ_vn_news)
    participant QD2 as Qdrant<br/>(econ_knowledge)
    participant RR as Reranker Service
    participant LLM as vLLM (remote)
    participant TTS as TTS Service

    User->>WebUI: 🎤 Voice message (WAV)
    WebUI->>Orch: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(multipart: audio + response_format=text+audio)

    rect rgb(255, 240, 240)
        Note over Orch: normalize_input → detect audio
        Orch->>ASR: POST /transcribe (audio bytes)
        Note over ASR: Load model if idle<br/>(cold start ~5-8s)
        ASR-->>Orch: {"text": "GDP Việt Nam năm 2023?"}
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Orch: input_guard
        Orch->>Guard: POST /classify (role=input)
        Guard-->>Orch: {"label": "safe"}
    end

    rect rgb(240, 240, 255)
        Note over Orch: embed
        Orch->>Emb: POST /embed (query, is_query=true)
        Emb-->>Orch: {"embeddings": [1024d vector]}
    end

    rect rgb(255, 255, 240)
        Note over Orch: retrieve (multi-collection, parallel)
        par Search both collections
            Orch->>QD1: hybrid_search(dense+sparse, top-10)
            QD1-->>Orch: 10 chunks from news
        and
            Orch->>QD2: hybrid_search(dense+sparse, top-10)
            QD2-->>Orch: 10 chunks from knowledge<br/>(may include chart/table chunks)
        end
        Note over Orch: Merge 20 candidates
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 255)
        Note over Orch: rerank
        Orch->>RR: POST /rerank (query, 20 passages)
        RR-->>Orch: top-5 scored
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
        Note over Orch: generate
        Orch->>LLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(system prompt + context + query)
        LLM-->>Orch: "GDP Việt Nam năm 2023 đạt 5.05%..."
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Orch: output_guard
        Orch->>Guard: POST /classify (role=output)
        Guard-->>Orch: {"label": "safe"}
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 240)
        Note over Orch: format_output (audio requested)
        Orch->>TTS: POST /synthesize (answer text)
        Note over TTS: Load model if idle
        TTS-->>Orch: audio/wav bytes
    end

    Orch-->>WebUI: SSE stream: text + citations<br/>+ audio (base64 WAV)
    WebUI-->>User: 📝 Text answer + 🔊 Audio playback
